name: JuliaOS
description: JuliaOS is a high-performance, open-source operating system for AI agents and swarms, designed to power the next era of autonomous software in Web3. Built with the Julia programming language, it enables real-time, cross-chain execution of intelligent agents for DeFi, trading, governance, and more. JuliaOS is an infrastructure layer where modular agents coordinate like swarms in nature to solve complex tasks without centralized control.
